00:09:24.220 --> 00:09:25.950 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: To get
these pipelines done.

00:09:25.950 --> 00:09:27.575 align:middle line:84%
>>SHEEHAN: To get
the pipeline through,

00:09:27.575 --> 00:09:29.020 align:middle line:84%
to help this
private corporation.

00:09:29.020 --> 00:09:31.600 align:middle line:84%
This private corporation
has made a decision

00:09:31.600 --> 00:09:34.630 align:middle line:84%
to move the pipeline from
where they intentionally

00:09:34.630 --> 00:09:39.460 align:middle line:84%
planned to have it made,
10 miles north of Bismarck,

00:09:39.460 --> 00:09:42.100 align:middle line:90%
a 93% white community.

00:09:42.100 --> 00:09:43.720 align:middle line:10%
