00:45:37.245 --> 00:45:38.045 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: So true.

00:45:38.045 --> 00:45:39.910 align:middle line:84%
>>SHEEHAN: And it's
already come to that.

00:45:39.910 --> 00:45:43.070 align:middle line:84%
We are looking it right in the
face in this administration.

00:45:43.070 --> 00:45:47.800 align:middle line:84%
This is an administration that
is attempting to hand over

00:45:47.800 --> 00:45:50.920 align:middle line:84%
the control and all the
instrumentalities of government

00:45:50.920 --> 00:45:53.620 align:middle line:84%
to the benefit of
private corporations.

00:45:53.620 --> 00:45:55.764 align:middle line:84%
And we are looking
at it right now.

00:45:55.764 --> 00:45:57.430 align:middle line:84%
And we are standing
in that exact moment

00:45:57.430 --> 00:45:59.770 align:middle line:84%
that that judge that
